Note:
    Please modify arguments(ADDR,ip,port,usr,psd) to match your test environment  before test.
    The test environment needs set up ftp.

    Argument:
        ip : socket and ftp ip
        port : socket port
        ADDR : socket addr
        usr : ftp username
        psd : tfp password
        dir_path : file path
        filename_fw : fw file name

Usage:
    1.run socket_server.py
    2.run test code : python socket_server_demo.py,python socket_client_demo.py
